{"id":"2aa1ec37-009a-4761-b141-4b4486bdadef","name":"-MHARP- \"1000.0\" (TKN HVY)","description":"<p>Since this is the biggest bot I made on this site...<br>Let's go from Version 2.0 to Version <span style=\"color: #fb4700\">1000</span>!<br><br>I must thank you all for this outrageous, outstanding, insane, and exquisite milestone...<br><span style=\"color: #fb4700\">1000</span> individual chats...! <span style=\"color: #fb4700\">1000</span> individual realms of complete nonsensical stories!<br><br><br><br><br>-My Hero Academia RP- (Bonus Pics)<br><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/240LmwyD2ZbB5n5XDZcNr.webp?width=1000\"><span style=\"color: #fb4700\">1000</span> chats, 150 away from 850!<br><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/l12r-5Xls8FvfS1EDBhJH.webp?width=1000\">20,000 chats, this bot got 20,000 chats on April Fools.<br><br><br><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/64936eeb-26fc-46b6-841c-0f41b54d2a6a_e8e3adf3-cd92-45e8-845e-2874d069b690.webp?width=1000\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><em>My Hero Academia's Class 1-A shines in recent [2023] Halloween fanart (Image via. Shueisha)</em></span><br>Artist, <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><em>X = </em></span><a href=\"https://x.com/ryosuketarou\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><em>@ryosuketarou</em></span></a><br>--<br><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/64936eeb-26fc-46b6-841c-0f41b54d2a6a_f4c1b64a-5300-4521-8dcd-40e272d73cc8.webp?width=1000\">Manga illustration from chapter 367, colored, my personal favorite<br>Artist, X = @<a href=\"https://x.com/horikoshiko?ref_src=twsrc%5Egoogle%7Ctwcamp%5Ese